OL,3,C'I was 17 and writing my will after
OL,4,Cdoctors tried to hide my HIV diagnosis'
OL,6,FWatch Martin's story...
OL,8,FA man who was 17 when he found out he
OL,9,Fwas HIV positive, learned decades
OL,10,Flater that doctors had tried to keep
OL,11,Fhis diagnosis a secret from him.
OL,13,FMartin Beard from found out he was HIV
OL,14,Fpositive in 1986, after being infected
OL,15,Fwith contaminated blood 'Factor VIII'
OL,16,Fwhen he was treated for a knee bleed
OL,17,Fthe year before.
OL,19,FHe was told he had just two years left
OL,20,Fto live.
