OL,6,FMartin attended a doctor's appointment
OL,7,Fwith his mother, when he found out
OL,8,Fabout his HIV.
OL,10,FHe said: "We haven't even sat down,
OL,11,Fthe door's still open and (the doctor)
OL,12,Fjust looks at me and says 'Hello, I
OL,13,Fsee you're HIV positive'.
OL,15,FHe adds: "It didn't really register
OL,16,Fwith me because I was a pretty healthy
OL,17,Fteenager. I just looked at him and
OL,18,Fsaid 'Oh well, that's life'.
