OL,6,FHis medical notes were sent to him and
OL,7,Famong them, he found a letter from
OL,8,F1985 - a year before he was told that
OL,9,Fhe was HIV positive.
OL,11,FHe said: "The letter is basically
OL,12,Fsaying that between doctors - Martin's
OL,13,Fbeen to see us with a bleed in his
OL,14,Fknee.
OL,16,F"We injected him with 1060 units of
OL,17,FFactor VIII, and he will return to the
OL,18,Fcentre if he has any further problems.
