OL,6,FHe was treated the year after finding
OL,7,Fout he was HIV positive and was put in
OL,8,Fisolation on a ward, with staff
OL,9,Fdressed in protective clothing when
OL,10,Fthey brought him food.
OL,12,FMartin said he even had to inject
OL,13,Fhimself, as staff wouldn't make up the
OL,14,Fsyringes or inject him themselves.
OL,16,F"It was such a scary feeling being in
OL,17,Fa new hospital, in isolation and you
OL,18,Fwere kind of just shut away..."
