OL,6,FMartin tells ITV News that in an ideal
OL,7,Fworld there'd be some justice, but for
OL,8,Fsomeone to be held accountable is
OL,9,F"highly impossible".
OL,11,FHe says there are people who've lost
OL,12,Floved ones, businesses, homes - and
OL,13,Fthe important thing for him is that it
OL,14,Fcan never ever happen again to anyone.
OL,16,F"Justice has to be served".
